SUBROUTINE u2_nextbook(id)
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  @@Name        : u2_nextbook 
*  @@Description : Accumulator for book numbers 
*  @@Version     : 1.0
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  Brief Description
*  -----------------
*  @@INFO
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  Warnings
*  --------
*
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
*  Modification History
*  --------------------
*  @@Log  
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Keywords
* --------
*
* --------------------------------------------------------------------------
* To Do List
* ----------
*
* --------------------------------------------------------------------------  
$OPTIONS PICK
Temp = 0
Open 'U2_PARAMS' To FL Then
ReadU Temp From FL, 'NEXT_TITLE' Else
Temp = ''
End
Temp += 1
Write Temp On FL, 'NEXT_TITLE'
End
id = Temp
RETURN
